    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i tried feathering it but the edges are still a bit obvious. also, do i need to worry about the stuff behind the wall causing issues, like if there's any weirdness or gaps in the framing that might show up through the mud later?",
      "source": "evaluator",
